fem.components

Class Node

  • java.lang.Object
    • util.model.NamedObject
      • fem.components.Node
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    INode, java.io.Externalizable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable, INamedObject, IStreamable

    public class Node
extends NamedObject
implements INode
    This class is abstract with super class INode. Class contains generic get and set methods required for implementing a node into the FemModel.
    Author:
    Darren Sulon
